CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 4, 1956, page A11, reads: "Youthful Hostesses... all daughters of members of the famous Frogs Club, had fun along with their guests at the party for their own set on Monday night at the Loendi Club. Luella Blow, this year's "Miss Derby Day," seated is surrounded by Rose Alice Cephas, Phyllis Garland, Sylvia Harris and Roberta Ratcliffe. - Teenie Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left, standing: Rose Alice Cephas, Phyllis Garland, Sylvia Harris, and Roberta Ratcliffe; seated: Luella Blow; wearing circular FROGS tags, gathered on porch of the Loendi Club for FROGS event
